    facts: ["Susak is the only sand island in the Adriatic — all others are limestone karst","The Susak dialect is so distinct from Croatian that linguists debate whether it is a separate language","The traditional Susak female costume with short red skirts is unique in Croatia — unlike any other regional dress","Susak has significant diaspora in New Jersey — emigrants maintained their unique culture in America","Susak's sand was laid down at the end of the last Ice Age, when the Adriatic was dry land and Susak a sand dune."],
