    facts: ["Lošinj has 1,100+ plant species — more than many countries much larger than it","The Adriatic Dolphin Project has been tracking individual dolphins near Lošinj since 1987","The island was declared a 'health island' by the Austro-Hungarian Medical Association in 1892","Mali Lošinj was the second-most photographed harbour in the pre-WWI Adriatic after Dubrovnik","Lošinj's 18th and 19th-century sea captains brought back plants from distant lands that thrived in its mild climate."],
