    facts: ["The ancient Greek bronze Apoxyomenos found in the sea near Lošinj in 1999 is one of the world's finest ancient bronzes","The statue dates from the 2nd century BC — it was lost at sea for 2,100 years before discovery","The Veli Lošinj museum was purpose-built to display the Apoxyomenos in optimal conservation conditions","Veli Lošinj's Venetian tower above the harbour dates from the 14th century","The Apoxyomenos bronze was found at just 45m depth by an Austrian diver on a recreational dive in 1999."],
