    didYouKnow: "The Keglević family of Sveti Križ Začretje were close enough to the Habsburg court that one of their daughters, Babette Keglević, was a piano student of Beethoven in Vienna in the 1790s — Beethoven dedicated his Piano Concerto No. 1 to her.",
