    facts: ["Nerezine's Franciscan monastery was founded in 1473 by Friar Martin of Osor","The village sits on the slopes of Mount Osoršćica (Televrina), the highest point on Lošinj at 588 metres","Nerezine is administratively part of the City of Mali Lošinj","The settlement is near the Osor canal that separates Lošinj from Cres","The Franciscan monastery library historically held significant ecclesiastical manuscripts"],
