    facts: ["Belej is in the sparsely populated southern part of Cres, in Primorje-Gorski Kotar County","Sheep-farming on the surrounding karst pastures has been the dominant traditional economic activity","Cres lamb (cresjska janjetina) and Cres cheese (cresjski sir) are recognised regional foods","The village is administratively part of the City of Mali Lošinj on the neighbouring island","Belej is surrounded by the long dry-stone walls that have subdivided Cres pastures for centuries"],
