    facts: ["Vinišće's name comes from vino (wine) — the village historically lived from viticulture and olives","The settlement administratively belongs to the Marina municipality in Split-Dalmatia County","The bay of Vinišće is one of the deepest natural harbours between Trogir and Rogoznica","The parish church of Saint Peter sits on the western shore of the bay","Vinišće's long, sheltered bay has long served Croatian sailors as a natural overnight anchorage on the Šibenik–Trogir passage."],
